mtr:GCST90200243_GCST90200115 a mtr:MetaboliteRatio ;
    rdfs:label "hydroxypalmitoyl sphingomyelin (d18:1/16:0(oh))** to n-palmitoyl-heptadecasphingosine (d17:1/16:0)*" ;
    mtr:llm_gene_phenotype_relationship "  The APOA1 pQTL colocalization suggests a causal link between APOA1 and the ratio. APOA1 is central to HDL metabolism and reverse cholesterol transport, processes in which sphingomyelins are involved.[10](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFJf4M3d5iHROAq5HBB0DOnvCJaufaVrlDi0304F9da2UPNCUZoMZOMj5JZZFRTcHj_o4ZucjPbiuiMOsPcBP23gxv3Fu3VPOeGqJsUOdB6BXmTl7TlbrBssvE65kSlErtqTy5q), [11](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFcXkO9TdOMtlhM7jwnoDqTyXmC82h6HUJ0Pn00hDZgKAqZmeIQDm-ome4w2KSr1HAPnlpwh7LGnba4sAdWSClUbuukRullfeZtlKZrqDyws3XWGe6O1Ph-rD-PKPHPkLq2A8Q=), [12](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGNdMAuK1g-a-kNjfGPiHzbf-vYOTPN8ep7a4tl___KRijrL8eVat436tNNYbVUkdAh2ncRJwPx-bvmqWiIW-Mjzo6SyyYn-cvYtbHBj4__JgAhBfPhtwRco3EXnFdy8zhz49A4Gkdl9O0oedTKXkm8i3X1cjdt5w==) Dysregulation of both APOA1 and sphingolipids is associated with cardiovascular diseases, the observed phenotypes.[13](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHpFZ2Ci5-tRk6Fufc_qSaf5P4mLduMQva3boqcoqILIeWvqBXse6ejf_nLFIyAiiDP-A7IpwFvIHQQ91XoJCQl9clT0wmeCVYM4-wCnhCh9CNDhvBsW9mm4keJhUces9yc9RsL), [7](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH6O13UMuovJduHVIN64BXVq9b4mblf2gIB_se1khRelnItPtkHFLdQkC7dZHP_OTR1S_2Mo9X1eWkIObbm4D6Fw-rdsMN5nORItZJqVB0IasSxz_APxsbRL-d10xiJOtOMT7hamJtq9LzPJ48=), [14](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG_4PB8wwmVZ74B-XIB3hGj1bmGbLMw_JuQZKT5gwGsN3uq91EQ9ZGf_YHCjTeiRDZMNdb59--afOXVJdCF_YsYjHPKZ_sJ1v5sPtzV2RxiqYORzBEV1LsuFCaFRDMCZUAWRpxXP9-IlaEsi8gDE1ZegmrcSnPlAUVtTXWscEPvNnOXlX254QpS8Dvx5lsFe9Gd2j98bbwJ39Rf-vUjUQPxkJwV_XYEn7ZIe_f1I9OaY8C5FbgMM8KUA1kKS5kgsw5grQ==), [15](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHgLmzhB8BRmjqHLKic8pXJCLMN4FLrtyCwimSneXU1za-nqn3lF7fnoXY8HfpLhomks108X9BdgTbBiDRcj1Jkr8TMf4e_99jCSacA699fYkoC694mHLmmcu2-lgfv6HRDCWuTIsW0WjZoTJdpBzd3zB5jZ4rLb_Xj_xK7NGv8Ou1rkrg2eTJ6N9qWr0KEto4CpS0EnqX63WDlKMuyeLQ=)  " ;
