mtr:GCST90199876_GCST90199733 a mtr:MetaboliteRatio ;
    rdfs:label "palmitoyl sphingomyelin (d18:1/16:0) to 1-palmitoyl-gpc (16:0)" ;
    mtr:has_denominator chebi:72998 ;
    mtr:has_numerator chebi:78646 ;
    mtr:llm_gene_phenotype_relationship " GCKR variants are associated with altered glucose/lipid metabolism and phenotypes like type 2 diabetes and hypercholesterolaemia.[1](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEFnCa2f17s2ttIlIJi3gZBxJqAfS8AIjAV85F1I0d9fsrPjVoLdg4R5V6obfef1dqQykOl7kdQO9tVpTmaeyQk8FuewB1DI-L0hKkLaW8M8X9XNV0j8a8FaNSYVTNXgT0lYn0qnYsCVWyF3HxWfA==), [2](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGFFFQ4f_kIiijn1j6Uzx3J77Y4_3z5Xe32LbUz8sBe23BIN_FZ7EdU68yMEbs1kVlqjaXr7vKh4KTPTLusI_SUtOokSUB8VabBKsW-zj-GUp7XCFsdV7d-W0Yn2MxKWDb6QeQqc_d8BBjC7M6fZjqLtX3oJLWWVO0=), [3](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQER7HB51n2SGqEau2CV2dPbjD0f2f0V8eFg705KpPyi-rXiMrJQ6fPLAMV-vITmdGhNLmsQsg4h_wALFjgBTqdjMdu8gS2YHJqzYnHB77zX4ax4GsoVYjPvYpBsZind3MIAH8KeRpjjnDT-pm_0naNpuxnpgEvid8Jy6sXSRIP2afwz2QwHC9uy1pncM-RZW9sxZYPbbrw=) This dysregulation likely affects the balance between sphingolipid and glycerophospholipid pools, leading to the observed ratio change and contributing to cardiometabolic diseases. " ;
    mtr:llm_phenotype_driver " Gene-centric:GCKR" ;
    mtr:llm_ratio_evidence " metabolites related through biology " ;
    mtr:llm_ratio_explanation " An increased ratio of palmitoyl sphingomyelin to 1-palmitoyl-gpc suggests a shift in lipid metabolism, potentially from GCKR-influenced altered glucose and lipid homeostasis.[1](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEFnCa2f17s2ttIlIJi3gZBxJqAfS8AIjAV85F1I0d9fsrPjVoLdg4R5V6obfef1dqQykOl7kdQO9tVpTmaeyQk8FuewB1DI-L0hKkLaW8M8X9XNV0j8a8FaNSYVTNXgT0lYn0qnYsCVWyF3HxWfA==), [3](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQER7HB51n2SGqEau2CV2dPbjD0f2f0V8eFg705KpPyi-rXiMrJQ6fPLAMV-vITmdGhNLmsQsg4h_wALFjgBTqdjMdu8gS2YHJqzYnHB77zX4ax4GsoVYjPvYpBsZind3MIAH8KeRpjjnDT-pm_0naNpuxnpgEvid8Jy6sXSRIP2afwz2QwHC9uy1pncM-RZW9sxZYPbbrw=) " ;
    mtr:max_pgain "630794169.670944"^^xsd:float .

