    mtr:llm_ratio_evidence " metabolites not in a pathway but enzyme catalyzes one metabolite " ;
    mtr:llm_ratio_explanation " NPL directly catabolizes the numerator, n-acetylneuraminate.[7](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGi3eEYR5Bmk5mbCXZvlzWBFZtrZwuM6CA87WouGj4cWz45LvFhSKHEWQ4h2EXDblMZS-QTZAyepLgZCT2uRgy_9E-IqiQwoqyE2MB4CyT-YctpXAxQCsECYzCqwctyRW6u63QvEoxVILiVKwEYIKH67gpsq32i8MhcOOSVt_KnR3tAcfxNpkuKZa_p1BRplQZ-Nt48l4ic-82iMaSlscssN1rvkEc3hRspyAcHeAgMwKjU6TAd5SKiJAKcvLxUItiU0SGyDg==) Pseudouridine is involved in separate RNA metabolic pathways and is not directly related to NPL's function.[5](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHUXLFV1aGLpCSGD6yD-9sGxmHN9U2iMl1XWTjln9rqYk4_87TJN6ZH--i_gPXEIMfU7zpTpmTngLgl38QCwMEMGxw4PeeI5zWdEOYguTZHmwxAq7JeemR49M5LmJy0uRXIi_DP5CkvSclh38odHINhH9NZUWxGQs1D9gGVfu-mCLRNydz8vSP88xWW-Z2MSvXkfIn2GnInCYgSAxg3a6qP5tNL5XZ8), [8](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGPPPZul8DxizgF0k8xqKmufw8Sc78HFZvNfmfKsq5hJHjE9u0b5smZZrKgCtUcxmF3ZCRR_Q4YjYV4xnz6q5k6NTD-o51dfvpra_ELMZ3-l7WWjFi7c9r2cMO8eDL01oG9k9EQLsPpvFktlA==) " ;
