    mtr:llm_ratio_evidence " metabolites not in a pathway but enzyme catalyzes one metabolite " ;
    mtr:llm_ratio_explanation " The ratio reflects the balance between glycerophospholipid and sphingolipid synthesis, potentially influenced by FADS1/FADS2-mediated fatty acid availability for their respective biosynthetic pathways. " ;
    mtr:max_pgain "88149879632.02847"^^xsd:float .

